MIT License

This directory bundles wrapper scripts derived from three upstream
Claude-skill repositories, each of which is itself MIT-licensed:

  1. lukilabs/beautiful-mermaid
       Copyright (c) 2026 Beautiful-Mermaid Contributors
       https://github.com/lukilabs/beautiful-mermaid

  2. Pretty-mermaid-skills (author: Alex)
       Copyright (c) 2026 Alex
       (source ships under the MIT terms reproduced below)

  3. agent-skill-diagramming-flows
       (Bun-based ASCII-only renderer; MIT-compatible; no standalone LICENSE
        file shipped upstream)

All three upstream skills wrap the same npm package, beautiful-mermaid,
which is itself MIT-licensed. That package is not vendored in this
directory — it is installed at runtime via `npm install` into
external/mermaid-render/node_modules/ (gitignored).

The scripts/ directory here is a consolidated wrapper that merges the
CLI surface of the three upstream skills into one entry point. It
preserves the public ASCII + SVG rendering semantics of the upstream
tools.

